Full Description: Offervana is platform technology company that bridges the gap for home sellers between iBuyers and selling homes the traditional way. Offervana's proprietary multioffer platform gives the consumer the ability to see all their iBuyer offer in one place helping them make a more informed decision. The company delivers full transparency of iBuyer fees, estimated net proceeds, comps used to price their property, and local market trends. The consumer can enter their address, complete the home survey, and with a click of a button submit their property to receive multiple cash offers from national iBuyers like Offerpad, Opendoor, and Zillow Offers alongside several other local investors who buy homes for cash. Offervana saves the consumer hours of submitting to multiple different iBuyers who buy homes for cash. Offervana also allows the consumer to try selling their home on the open market and then switch back to selling their home to an iBuyer without incurring agent fees or broker contract cancellation fees.
